        <updateDate>2018-08-08T23:44:52Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Allied Burden Sharing Report Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill directs the Department of Defense to submit an annual report to Congress describing: </p> <ul> <li>each allied nation's annual defense spending, its contributions to military or stability operations in which the United States participates, and limitations it places on such contributions' use; and </li> <li>actions taken by the United States or by other countries to minimize such limitations. </li> </ul>]]></text>
      </summary>
